    {
      "id": "PopularPost320380",
      "post_content": "@Paleopaladin  \nPeople hate-rate cards that are expensive because it shows a failure in design. If a card is so good that it sells for 20x other cards do that you consider good, then why was it even printed?  \n  \nAlso, swords aren't really to make your creatures resistant to removal. That's just an added bonus. The sword make it so **any** creature you equip suddenly turns into a huge threat if unblocked. The protection mostly just gives evasion to make them even more annoying.  \n  \nThis sword, while giving the least advantage, provides a really scary clock.",
      "posted_by": "SAUS3",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost320380\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@Paleopaladin<br/>People hate-rate cards that are expensive because it shows a failure in design. If a card is so good that it sells for 20x other cards do that you consider good, then why was it even printed?<br/><br/>Also, swords aren't really to make your creatures resistant to removal. That's just an added bonus. The sword make it so <b>any</b> creature you equip suddenly turns into a huge threat if unblocked. The protection mostly just gives evasion to make them even more annoying.<br/><br/>This sword, while giving the least advantage, provides a really scary clock.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy98122\">SAUS3</span>\r\n                                (6/7/2013 7:46:57 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSm